73
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:43,860
Yes.

74
00:07:44,450 --> 00:07:45,600
I admit

75
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:47,070
that everything was my doing.

76
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,270
I did all that.

77
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,070
What can you do about it?

78
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:51,800
What can you do about it?

79
