How?

109
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,100
Everyone likes you, Lin Wanxing.

110
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,200
So I decided to destroy you
with my own hands.

111
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,320
I swore to push you into a mire

112
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,650
and make sure
you could never get out of it.

113
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:04,070
When this information is posted online

114
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,000
and gaining traction...

115
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,960
Gossip is a fearful thing.

116
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,170
By then,

117
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:08,990
your reputation will be ruined.

118
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:11,910
He's just a dark and ugly rat

119
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:13,670
