203
00:14:27,370 --> 00:14:28,460
I must not lose.

204
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:32,600
But now I've thought it through.

205
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:36,100
I don't have to be so harsh on myself.

206
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:38,260
Being alive itself

207
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,060
