208
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:47,630
There is no such thing as healing
in the world.

209
00:14:48,670 --> 00:14:51,360
Pain leaves scars in our hearts.

210
00:14:52,660 --> 00:14:55,320
So, amidst confusion and perplexity,
we need to

211
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:57,710
