226
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:45,220
I'll go handle this in the kitchen first.

227
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:48,240
Did you miss us?

228
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:50,660
We'll take you to the beach
with us next time, alright?

229
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:51,660
Good boy.

230
00:15:58,360 --> 00:15:58,840
Hello.

231
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:03,840
Your dad's coming.

232
00:16:12,940 --> 00:16:13,750
Dad,

233
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,320
