234
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:27,910
Those are clothes.

235
00:16:27,910 --> 00:16:29,510
Clothes I bought for Ms. Lin.

236
00:16:30,730 --> 00:16:32,660
Why did you buy these many clothes?

237
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,270
Ms. Lin is going to the battlefield soon.

238
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:36,000
I'm here to deliver gear to her.

239
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:38,120
She's going to court,

240
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,280
