243
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:44,000
Girls all like pretty clothes.

244
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,120
Right, Ms. Lin?

245
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:49,240
Anyway, I've brought the clothes here.

246
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,240
Just accept them.

247
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:54,050
Whether you'll wear them or not...
It's just a kind gesture from me.

248
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:55,720
Thank you for such kindness, Uncle.

249
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,790
Please don't go to any expense
on my account next time.

250
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:59,080
You see, my tiny house

251
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:00,740
can barely hold so many items.

252
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,600
I can get you a new...

253
