Please don't buy me any houses,
either.

254
00:17:07,109 --> 00:17:08,240
Well, then, Ms. Lin,

255
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,480
t-tell me what you like,

256
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,740
