257
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,160
Actually,

258
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:14,550
I enjoy delicious food.

259
00:17:14,550 --> 00:17:15,160
How about this?

260
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,750
I'll treat everyone to a meal next time.

261
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:17,400
Sounds great.

262
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,720
I'm a food enthusiast too.

263
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:19,400
It's settled then.

264
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,790
When you win this lawsuit,

265
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,160
