266
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:24,400
We'll provide feasts
for three days and nights.

267
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,440
-Thank you, Uncle.
-Cut that crap.

268
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:29,270
Dad, aren't you going to
visit Yueyang Tower with Mom?

269
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:31,440
Hurry up and memorize
the Record of Yueyang Tower.

270
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,550
I did forget about it.

271
00:17:32,550 --> 00:17:33,280
You did, huh?

272
00:17:33,590 --> 00:17:34,920
Had better get a move on.

273
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:36,350
Bye bye then!

274
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,270
Don't buy clothes for her
with your taste again.

275
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:40,000
Got it.

276
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:47,160
Your dad has a more lovely personality
than you.

277
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,350
It's rare to see a wealthy

278
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:50,030
