You've got this.

818
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:53,270
Come on, I'll give you a tour.

819
00:40:54,550 --> 00:40:56,110
Are you sure you can manage?

820
00:40:56,350 --> 00:40:57,350
Yes!

821
00:40:57,380 --> 00:40:58,300
What is this?

822
00:41:01,150 --> 00:41:02,280
Feel free to browse.

823
00:41:05,250 --> 00:41:06,690
Is this your room.

824
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:10,110
I could tell that.

825
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:18,630
What a spacious room.

826
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:30,230
Have you always looked so grumpy
since you were little?

827
00:41:30,230 --> 00:41:32,230
It's just that my smiles are subtle.

828
00:41:33,770 --> 00:41:34,900
I have other photos.

829
00:41:35,190 --> 00:41:36,120
Care to see them?

830
00:41:36,190 --> 00:41:36,960
Sure.

831
00:41:48,670 --> 00:41:50,070
Is this you?

832
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:54,670
I didn't know you used to be a chubby kid.

833
00:41:55,830 --> 00:41:57,360
It was thanks to my grandma.

834
00:41:57,710 --> 00:41:58,590
My grandma's dream grandson

835
00:41:58,590 --> 00:42:00,190
had to be well-fed and plump.

836
00:42:03,960 --> 00:42:05,880
Why is this photo still here?

837
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,510
Move your hand.

838
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:14,040
Let me see.

839
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:18,510
Is this also you,

840
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:20,000
a boy in a princess dress?

841
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:21,550
Little did I imagine you'd like

842
00:42:21,550 --> 00:42:23,840
to become a princess when you were little.

843
00:42:23,840 --> 00:42:26,530
This is the proof of me being persecuted
by Wang Tian.

844
00:42:26,530 --> 00:42:27,550
Being persecuted?

845
00:42:27,550 --> 00:42:29,070
It seems to me the look suits you well.

846
00:42:29,070 --> 00:42:30,510
A pink bow.

847
00:42:30,510 --> 00:42:31,440
A white tulle gown.

848
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:32,960
And those Mary Jane shoes.

849
00:42:33,590 --> 00:42:35,190
You look really cute in them.

850
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,760
Rainbow-like long hair,

851
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,510
with eyes resembling jewels.

852
00:42:39,510 --> 00:42:42,770
I think Her Highness
the Shining Star Genius is even cuter.

853
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:44,320
Why haven't you forgotten it?

854
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,190
I just can't,

855
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:48,030
for she is so impressive and unforgettable

856
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:50,830
that the memory about her
is still vivid in my mind.

857
00:42:51,070 --> 00:42:52,030
Fine then.

858
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:54,000
It's fair to say we have seen each other's

859
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:55,150
embarrassing past.

860
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:56,840
We're even now.

861
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:00,760
Why did you put on those red flowers?

862
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:03,420
It was all because I was persecuted
by Wang Tian.

863
00:43:06,320 --> 00:43:08,850
You grew up to be
quite a handsome guy, though.

864
00:43:35,370 --> 00:43:36,690
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

865
00:43:37,850 --> 00:43:39,170
♪ Because you're with me ♪

